1
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,630
We're a hotel by Thai people,

2
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:26,150
so we still need to exhibit Thai charm.

3
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,550
I'm happy

4
00:02:28,970 --> 00:02:30,740
that my Moo-Moo

5
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:35,080
is working this hard for our hotel.

6
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,600
Well, if you see him every day,

7
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:41,810
you'll have a chance to do
something shitty in front of him,

8
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:44,256
so that he'll change his mind
and go for someone else.

9
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,720
Just because he seems familiar
doesn't mean I'm into him.

10
00:02:47,330 --> 00:02:48,330
- Whoa!
- Whoa!

11
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,920
Hey,

12
00:02:52,290 --> 00:02:53,290
don't be mad.

13
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:54,730
I can buy you a new one.

14
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,910
My dad bought that book for me.

15
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,510
It's not the same even if you do.

16
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,400
An influencer is coming
to review our hotel!

17
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,240
Here, I think
you definitely know who this is.

18
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,310
Hello, Jang, Gift.

19
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,970
- Hello.
- Hello.

20
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:24,030
Ooh, the influencer whom
we signed a contract has arrived!

21
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:25,990
I'm excited, Jang!

22
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,360
Surprise!

23
00:03:54,170 --> 00:03:55,910
Wearing shades indoors. What a poser.

24
00:03:55,950 --> 00:03:57,090
What did you say, Moo?

25
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,020
Oh...

26
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:59,476
Nothing.
It's just that the voices in my head

27
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,036
are a little too loud.
It's nothing at all, Jang.

28
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:01,930
- Nothing at all.
- Oh...

29
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,690
Are you a housekeeper here, bestie?

30
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:06,460
I'm a housekeeper who tosses
a rotten banana down the trash

31
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,500
at this hotel,

32
00:04:08,270 --> 00:04:11,100
Kluayhom, you lovely... banana.

33
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,460
Oh, Kluayhom.

34
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,240
Long time no see, Fu.

35
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,800
I miss you.

36
00:04:16,150 --> 00:04:17,150
How have you been?

37
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,590
I've been well.

38
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:19,740
Honestly,

39
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:21,230
when you guys contacted me,

40
00:04:21,770 --> 00:04:23,140
I was thinking about...

41
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:24,110
not even charging you.

42
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,580
Oh, that won't do.

43
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,100
How could we let you do it for free?

44
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,090
Well, it could be something else in exchange.

45
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,530
For example...

46
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,440
free accommodation.

47
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,480
Oh...

48
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:39,260
Anything for you, Kluayhom.

49
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:41,590
Actually, if you ever feel like visiting...

50
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:43,020
just let me know.

51
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:44,740
Reach out to me, and I'll take care of it.

52
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:46,310
Sure thing.

53
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:47,800
Right, speaking of which...

54
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:49,900
You and Moo

55
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,420
already knew each other, right?

56
00:04:51,970 --> 00:04:53,140
Oh, yes.

57
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:55,580
We're so close.

58
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:57,000
Right, bestie?

59
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:59,680
Yes, totally so.

60
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:01,620
Yeah, that's nice.

61
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:02,936
It's great that you two are close friends.

62
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,060
In any case,

63
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,820
please take care

64
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:07,460
of Kluayhom for me.

65
00:05:07,770 --> 00:05:09,026
You're friends, so working together

66
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:12,180
is gonna be fun.

67
00:05:12,230 --> 00:05:14,060
It's totally gonna be fun.

68
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:18,000
Then, allow me to take Kluayhom
on a tour around the hotel.

69
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:18,960
I'll leave him to you.

70
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,630
Yes. This way, Kluayhom.

71
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,600
- See you later.
- See you.

72
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,260
Damn you, Fu.

73
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,590
Hi, girls...

74
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,040
Oh, my Gosh!

75
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:38,210
This is so luxurious and fancy, guys!

76
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:40,020
I love!

77
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,450
This is our hotel's finest room.

78
00:05:44,330 --> 00:05:47,220
This is as fancy
as a penthouse in New York.

79
00:05:48,010 --> 00:05:49,050
New York...

80
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,700
Please make yourself
comfortable, Kluayhom.

81
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,640
If you need something, you can tell Moo.

82
00:05:53,910 --> 00:05:54,380
Alright.

83
00:05:54,530 --> 00:05:56,660
Moo, please take care
of Kluayhom on my behalf.

84
00:05:56,740 --> 00:05:57,740
Sure thing.

85
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,000
I'll leave him to you.

86
00:06:05,670 --> 00:06:07,230
Long time no see.

87
00:06:07,370 --> 00:06:08,370
Have you been well?

88
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:09,810
I have.

89
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:12,340
How cold.

90
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:14,580
Don't you care that
your old friend will be sad?

91
00:06:15,490 --> 00:06:16,730
I don't have a friend like you.

92
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,280
Ugh!

93
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:19,870
Fine, then.

94
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,540
But today...

95
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:23,090
you're a hotel staff member.

96
00:06:23,770 --> 00:06:25,710
And I... am the guest.

97
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,380
So,

98
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,500
whatever I tell you to do,

99
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:29,560
you need to do it.

100
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,710
What are you standing around for?

101
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,080
Set up the lighting!

102
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:43,630
You think they hired you
just to stand there and watch me?

103
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,280
Chop-chop.

104
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,040
We have to film today.

105
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,100
Silly Moo, to the left!

106
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:54,850
Come over here.

107
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,820
I want the view over there.

108
00:06:58,620 --> 00:07:00,550
Higher. I don't want my face to be in the dark.

109
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,676
Why aren't you facing the light, then?

110
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:03,780
Open your damn eyes!

111
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:04,970
The view is over there!

112
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:06,980
Move.

113
00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:07,500
To the left.
Higher!

114
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:08,580
A little lower.
More towards the middle!

115
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,430
Alright, to the left.
Switch to the cool white light.

116
00:07:11,220 --> 00:07:13,020
Hold it in front of my face so it looks good.

117
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,040
Higher.

118
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,280
Great.

119
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:18,330
You just unplugged it!

120
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,520
Can the staff here

121
00:07:21,570 --> 00:07:22,570
do anything at all?

122
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,720
Ugh!

123
00:07:24,030 --> 00:07:25,200
How did they train you?

124
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,100
Oh!?

125
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:31,880
You already sighed?

126
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:34,390
The staff here has no patience, huh?

127
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:37,270
Guess I'll have to do
an honest review of this.

128
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:39,990
Just hold the light properly.

129
00:08:06,970 --> 00:08:08,100
I'm bummed.

130
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:10,810
They still don't seem to cave in.

131
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,100
Hm...

132
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:16,820
Wanna try being cold toward them?

133
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,100
Would it be a good idea?

134
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:22,130
What if they dislike me even more?

135
00:08:26,710 --> 00:08:29,210
I think you're making
too many moves on them.

136
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,140
Try being unwavering for once.

137
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:34,010
Maybe that'd make him feel lonely.

138
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,310
Fine... I'll give it a try.

139
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,220
Thank you, Tutor M.

140
00:08:44,870 --> 00:08:46,530
If that person still refuses to cave in,

141
00:08:47,070 --> 00:08:48,590
I'm gonna win you over for real, Tong.

142
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:49,880
Just you wait.

143
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,650
Go for it.

144
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,240
Tomo, I'm open here.

145
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:05,790
Tee, shoot!

146
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,630
One, two, three!

147
00:09:21,570 --> 00:09:23,880
Right, next up is this one, Mr. Fu.

148
00:09:25,650 --> 00:09:27,260
It's the list from the first group

149
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:29,990
that wants to redesign this part.

150
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:32,400
Next, I'll film in this zone.

151
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:34,750
This is fabulous. How pretty.

152
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:36,510
As for the light stand,

153
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,300
make sure it's ready.

154
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,040
- Sure.
- This is pretty.

155
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,240
Oh, Fu!

156
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,410
Hello.

157
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,560
Hello there.

158
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:56,100
Alright,

159
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:58,140
regarding the supplier,

160
00:09:58,180 --> 00:10:01,220
would you like to stick
with the same one or go with a new one?

161
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:03,240
I think I'll go with a new one.

162
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:04,780
Right here,

163
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:07,636
I think it's gonna look stunning
if I film down here.

164
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:08,780
That's done.

165
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,620
Bye-bye.

166
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:36,920
He doesn't seem to
care about you as much as he did.

167
00:10:38,190 --> 00:10:39,270
That's none of my business.

168
00:10:40,450 --> 00:10:41,680
Why the long face?

169
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:44,030
Don't tell me you're getting insecure.

170
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,720
Insecure? Why would I be?

171
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:47,340
Maybe he's getting fed up

172
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:49,320
with having to spoil you like he always has.

173
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,350
Come on, let's get to work.

174
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,870
Set that light stand up.

175
00:11:01,210 --> 00:11:02,580
Hey, what are you still doing?

176
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:09,770
How did these get here?

177
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,520
Hey, can I have this?

178
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:26,490
Moo, you also got some?

179
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:29,280
Fu's been giving these out to everyone.

180
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:33,250
Let's see.

181
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:36,980
What a bummer!

182
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,700
Where are all the grape-flavored ones?

183
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:42,550
- There's none?
- That flavor's the best of them all, too.

184
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,040
No idea.

185
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,680
- Mm...
- You're right.

186
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,310
I have none of those, either.

187
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,550
It's all yummy.

188
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,740
I'll take it home.

189
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,600
Give me the yellow one
if you still have some.

190
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:05,840
I've followed your advice, Tutor M.

191
00:12:06,380 --> 00:12:08,420
But acting indifferent
towards someone I'm into

192
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:10,500
is vewy hard to me.

193
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,840
Vewy hard...

194
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,400
Vewy hard...

195
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:18,030
Then... let's try Plan B.

196
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,800
Alright.

197
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,630
Make them a little jealous.

198
00:12:27,230 --> 00:12:28,350
I'll give it a go.

199
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,650
(To Kluayhom)

200
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,200
Where have you been?

201
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:10,060
We could lose the light.

202
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:11,500
Don't tell me...

203
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:15,150
you were blubbing because Fu
doesn't care about you anymore?

204
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:18,070
- Eat shit.
- Disgusting!

205
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:20,860
Hurry up and set up the lighting.
We're going to film now.

206
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,520
Your phone?

207
00:13:25,050 --> 00:13:26,140
Phone.

208
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:28,970
Film it nicely.

209
00:13:29,010 --> 00:13:30,530
I want beautiful, clear lighting.

210
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,330
Mm.

211
00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:32,880
Don't forget to pay attention.

212
00:13:37,330 --> 00:13:38,330
What's with this guy?

213
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:40,590
He was pouting just earlier.

214
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,720
Come on.

215
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,510
Let's film this angle.

216
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,540
Make sure it looks gorgeous.

217
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:48,130
Come on, bring that energy in.

218
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,660
Boost it up.

219
00:13:51,410 --> 00:13:52,410
Silly Moo!

220
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:55,730
Come on, Kluay.

221
00:13:55,990 --> 00:13:57,176
You don't want to be in the dark, right?

222
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:59,030
- Here, let me light it up for ya.
- Ugh!

223
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,030
Pay attention when you film!

224
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:01,130
I am paying attention!

225
00:14:01,170 --> 00:14:02,730
Keep in mind: I'm your guest today.

226
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,820
But you said you didn't like being in the dark.

227
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:07,270
- So I'm gonna light you up nice and close.
- Thanks.

228
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:09,130
I might as well just put on makeup!

229
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,930
Focus. Make sure it looks good.

230
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:13,940
Hello, everyone.
Right now, we're at Golden Peony Hotel.

231
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:15,626
I'm telling you,
this is such a beautiful hotel.

232
00:14:15,650 --> 00:14:17,660
The pool is, like, 400 acres.

233
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:19,070
Seriously, it's truly beautiful.

234
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:20,170
Follow me with the camera!

235
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,870
- Okay, okay.
- Take it out. Okay.

236
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:23,620
You guys, look at this.

237
00:14:23,660 --> 00:14:25,476
Where else could you find such a nice pool view

238
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,650
and skyscrapers like they have here?

239
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,570
Oh, I love.

240
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,240
Follow me.

241
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,816
- Do I look pretty?
- Your swimsuit, sure.

242
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,800
Focus!

243
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,780
- I am.
- Thank you, Moo.

244
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,500
Can I... Ugh! Moo!

245
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:44,780
- It's to brighten your face. Isn't that good?
- Yeah, it's already bright enough.

246
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:46,800
Moo, bestie, please do it properly.

247
00:14:46,970 --> 00:14:48,570
- Of course.
- Thanks.

248
00:14:48,610 --> 00:14:50,250
Guys, I really want you to check it out.

249
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:52,050
Come visit when you have time.

250
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:01,500
Hm...

251
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:03,440
Is there anything else
you want to update me on?

252
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,310
- It's Kluayhom.
- Oh...

253
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,220
Oh, Kluayhom!

254
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:08,500
Is everything all good?

255
00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:09,560
All good.

256
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,430
Thank you for the candies, Fu.

257
00:15:15,500 --> 00:15:17,500
Oh, these are from you?

258
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:18,960
Thank you.

259
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:24,180
By the way...

260
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:27,210
Where are all the grape-flavored ones?

261
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,480
What a bummer. Those are the best ones.

262
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,760
Ugh, nothing but the grape-flavored ones.

263
00:15:36,900 --> 00:15:37,700
What a bummer.

264
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,550
I don't even get to eat the other flavors.

265
00:15:42,370 --> 00:15:43,800
Oops, sorry.

266
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:46,300
Uh...

267
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:48,510
If everything is done,

268
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:49,820
this evening,

269
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:52,850
I would like to treat you
to dinner as a thank-you.

270
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,350
That sounds nice.

271
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:58,520
You're still as adorable as ever, Fu.

272
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:00,740
Anyway, excuse me

273
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:03,100
while I take a shower and get dolled up nicely.

274
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:04,870
Sure.

275
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:07,940
Jang, please take care
of our dinner this evening.

276
00:16:07,980 --> 00:16:08,980
Of course.

277
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:35,300
How have you been?

278
00:16:35,430 --> 00:16:36,430
Good?

279
00:16:37,370 --> 00:16:38,370
I've been good.

280
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,270
Thank you.

281
00:16:44,710 --> 00:16:46,910
Kluayhom, give this a try.

282
00:16:47,270 --> 00:16:48,340
This dish

283
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:50,670
was specifically designed
for this place by the chef.

284
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:56,780
Are you still into Moo?

285
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,440
Mm...

286
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:00,620
I would say.

287
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,930
After this long?

288
00:17:05,970 --> 00:17:06,970
Mm.

289
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,090
Well...

290
00:17:10,490 --> 00:17:12,330
But I guess
I'll have to try a little bit more.

291
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:13,900
What else could I do?

292
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:15,330
There's no stopping my heart now.

293
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,640
So he likes the grape-flavored ones.

294
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:12,990
Look at those hearts.

295
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:15,340
- How many? One, two, three, four, five...
- Uh...

296
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:16,500
Whoa, countless of them.

297
00:18:16,570 --> 00:18:17,570
Fu,

298
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:20,570
my name is Kluayhom.

299
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:23,050
Uh... here's for you.

300
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,160
Hey, I have to go.

301
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:27,950
Uh... thanks.

302
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,200
Uh...

303
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:32,790
Actually,

304
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:34,140
I like you.

305
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:38,750
Actually,

306
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:41,020
I'm allergic to certain artificial sweeteners,

307
00:18:41,150 --> 00:18:42,220
including...

308
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,070
the one used in this candy.

309
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:46,450
I can't eat it.

310
00:18:46,490 --> 00:18:47,920
Thank you, anyway.

311
00:18:48,450 --> 00:18:49,450
Sure.

312
00:18:53,770 --> 00:18:54,920
There's also some cake.

313
00:18:57,290 --> 00:18:58,730
Then, I should get going.

314
00:19:39,910 --> 00:19:42,500
No matter how many years,
you always look elsewhere.

315
00:19:43,170 --> 00:19:44,800
Hm? What was that?

316
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:48,970
Nothing.

317
00:19:50,580 --> 00:19:51,920
I'm just telling you that...

318
00:19:52,740 --> 00:19:53,740
It's time

319
00:19:53,780 --> 00:19:55,870
I make you look this way.

320
00:20:08,430 --> 00:20:09,510
It's to your liking, right?

321
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:10,800
It's delicious.

322
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:14,520
Oh?

323
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:15,590
Just the person I need.

324
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:18,800
So tomorrow, I'm filming
a dance video at the hotel.

325
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:20,490
Come give me a hand, would you?

326
00:20:22,330 --> 00:20:23,830
You should join me, Fu.

327
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:24,870
It's gonna be great.

328
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,200
But...

329
00:20:28,580 --> 00:20:29,790
I don't know how to dance.

330
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:31,800
It's fine. I'll teach you.

331
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:34,540
It's going to be absolutely viral,

332
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,780
and even more people
will want to stay at this hotel

333
00:20:37,060 --> 00:20:39,580
when the hotel owner
is such a cutie.

334
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:41,780
Am I right?

335
00:20:41,820 --> 00:20:42,850
Pretty please?

336
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:44,980
Please...

337
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,060
Alright, alright, alright.

338
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:47,270
I'll give it a try.

339
00:20:48,370 --> 00:20:49,370
There we go.

340
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,260
You're the cutest.

341
00:20:51,620 --> 00:20:54,220
Now I know what the vision
of new-generation hotel owners is like.

342
00:20:55,370 --> 00:20:56,370
I'll be waiting.

343
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,060
You rotten banana!

344
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,570
You and Kluayhom sure are
destined for each other.

345
00:21:06,810 --> 00:21:07,810
You tell me!

346
00:21:07,870 --> 00:21:10,100
He’s at your brother’s hotel
for a review right now.

347
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:12,270
Been seducing him for real.

348
00:21:13,310 --> 00:21:16,110
Maybe he's gonna turn up
as your brother-in-law.

349
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,780
So freaking extra.

350
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:20,510
But it's a good thing.

351
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,400
That way, my brother will leave you alone.

352
00:21:22,690 --> 00:21:24,510
But he's a horrible person.

353
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:28,320
Do you want your brother
to end up with someone like that?

354
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,530
Acting all like a well-wisher.

355
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:33,210
You're just a dog in the manger.
No!

356
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,880
I'm with Moo on this.

357
00:21:35,950 --> 00:21:37,760
Don't let Fu be with Kluayhom.

358
00:21:37,970 --> 00:21:38,970
What?

359
00:21:39,090 --> 00:21:40,450
You too, Tian?

360
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,000
Why not?

361
00:21:43,970 --> 00:21:45,340
What? Don't just ditch.

362
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,290
Come back and tell us.

363
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:48,380
(Self-Nurture)

364
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:28,410
Wait.

365
00:23:30,530 --> 00:23:31,170
Here.

366
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:32,930
New book, same cover.

367
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,180
I said I didn't want it.

368
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:38,630
This is not gonna be the same.

369
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:40,060
I know.

370
00:23:43,710 --> 00:23:45,320
That's why I brought these tools.

371
00:23:45,980 --> 00:23:48,080
I asked a book repair shop,

372
00:23:48,540 --> 00:23:50,120
and they've taught me the basics.

373
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:51,610
Let's repair it together.

374
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,666
Do you have to go all those extra miles?

375
00:23:53,690 --> 00:23:54,690
What?

376
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:57,150
I thought you said
your father gave it to you before he died.

377
00:23:57,410 --> 00:23:59,340
How dare you? My father is still alive!

378
00:24:01,690 --> 00:24:02,690
Oh...

379
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,740
Just...

380
00:24:06,260 --> 00:24:07,260
forget about it.

381
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:10,370
It'll never be the same.

382
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:11,940
So...

383
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:13,580
where is this new book you're giving me?

384
00:24:14,110 --> 00:24:15,110
Right.

385
00:24:16,950 --> 00:24:17,950
Here you go.

386
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:23,630
Anything else?

387
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:27,560
Not really.

388
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:59,630
After seeing me like this,

389
00:24:59,830 --> 00:25:01,130
is your heart finally trembling?

390
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:03,680
It's whatever.

391
00:25:04,630 --> 00:25:05,870
You don't may what you seen.

392
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:07,400
What now?

393
00:25:07,580 --> 00:25:08,780
"You don't mean what you say?"

394
00:25:08,870 --> 00:25:10,330
Hm, you get it.

395
00:25:11,570 --> 00:25:13,110
It's exactly what you're thinking.

396
00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:16,060
You still refuse to cave in.

397
00:25:16,500 --> 00:25:17,500
Hm?

398
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,420
You actually

399
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:28,940
have quite a nice figure.

400
00:25:29,410 --> 00:25:30,740
Thank you, Kluay.

401
00:25:33,700 --> 00:25:34,750
I'm so excited.

402
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:36,350
Come on, let's go live!

403
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,200
Let's go.

404
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:40,840
Come, now.

405
00:25:47,470 --> 00:25:49,140
Okay. Let's start rehearsing.

406
00:25:49,420 --> 00:25:51,420
You record the video, silly Moo.

407
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:52,680
- I'll leave it to you.
- Okay?

408
00:25:52,970 --> 00:25:54,700
So, to begin, our first move

409
00:25:54,740 --> 00:25:56,910
- is to hold up both fists.
- Hold them up like this?

410
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,900
- Oh, um... bring them closer to you.
- Closer.

411
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,196
You don't have to lean towards them.

412
00:26:00,220 --> 00:26:02,330
- Then jump in a circle.
- Jump.

413
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:05,640
- Yes, jump. Like that. Yes.
- In a circle.

414
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,100
Then we will...

415
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:11,220
- tap, tap, tap on our chest.
- Tap, tap.

416
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:13,540
Yeah, your arm should be
at that height. Good.

417
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,740
Okay, then touch your head.

418
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:17,340
Touch my head.

419
00:26:17,380 --> 00:26:19,960
- Then you thrust your hip.
- Thrust my hip...

420
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:21,140
Twice. Bam! Bam!

421
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,490
- One! Two!
- Or maybe like...

422
00:26:25,280 --> 00:26:26,280
What's the matter?

423
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:28,460
Uh... I just got dizzy.

424
00:26:28,780 --> 00:26:29,960
I'll take a restroom break.

425
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:32,180
Okay, go.

426
00:26:36,070 --> 00:26:37,890
- Hey... let's continue.
- Oh... yeah.

427
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:39,210
- Right.
- So the next one...

428
00:27:04,260 --> 00:27:05,260
What's wrong?

429
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,500
Nothing.

430
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:10,210
Are you jealous?

431
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:14,400
No.

432
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:18,260
If you're jealous, just say it.

433
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,700
Ugh, I said I wasn't!

434
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,990
How can there be a guy like this?

435
00:27:36,100 --> 00:27:37,770
So adorable, even when he's mad.

436
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:43,060
Oh... my poor heart is all melted.

437
00:27:43,770 --> 00:27:45,340
Alright, let's start our livestream.

438
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:47,800
You hold the light.

439
00:27:48,370 --> 00:27:49,370
Okay.

440
00:27:49,900 --> 00:27:50,900
We're starting...

441
00:27:51,090 --> 00:27:52,090
Three, two...

442
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,640
one.

443
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:56,260
Hello, everyone.

444
00:27:56,300 --> 00:27:59,780
I would like to welcome you to...

445
00:27:59,820 --> 00:28:02,740
'A Piece of Banana'!

446
00:28:02,780 --> 00:28:05,460
Today, we have a very handsome guest

447
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:07,250
who is also the owner of a hotel.

448
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:10,060
Please welcome Fu! Come here.

449
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:12,280
Hello.

450
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:13,820
Hello, everyone.

451
00:28:13,870 --> 00:28:15,070
Now, let's read some comments.

452
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:18,190
"Aw, they look so cute together."

453
00:28:18,470 --> 00:28:20,080
"You look so much like a couple."

454
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:21,890
Gosh, you guys.

455
00:28:22,670 --> 00:28:23,830
It's not all that much.

456
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,620
So today...

457
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:29,980
we're at the gym

458
00:28:30,020 --> 00:28:31,220
of Golden Peony Hotel.

459
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:34,860
If you like keeping your health
in check or prioritizing your wellbeing,

460
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:37,540
then this place is for you.
Please give it lots of love!

461
00:28:37,670 --> 00:28:38,700
Come and join us.

462
00:28:39,150 --> 00:28:41,780
So, for today,

463
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:44,000
since Fu is here with us,
we've gotta do something fun.

464
00:28:44,100 --> 00:28:46,450
We're going to dance today.

465
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:49,056
- We're dancing together, that's right.
- Dancing together?

466
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,080
Are you ready?

467
00:28:50,420 --> 00:28:52,630
- I'm ready.
- Let's show them what we've got.

468
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:54,320
Turn on the music!

469
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:58,650
Okay, are you ready?

470
00:29:04,059 --> 00:29:05,059
Let's stretch first.

471
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:07,160
Ready?

472
00:29:07,970 --> 00:29:09,800
Five, six, seven, eight...

473
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:18,070
Now, spin.

474
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:27,230
Turn off the music. Turn it off!

475
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:30,740
Are you alright, Moo?

476
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:32,900
Oh...

477
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:35,380
I also want to dance.

478
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,440
Is it okay if I join you?

479
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,860
I also feel like dancing.

480
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:42,420
You? Can you even dance, Moo?

481
00:29:42,510 --> 00:29:43,840
I don't think so.

482
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:46,350
I'm craving some clout, too.

483
00:29:46,790 --> 00:29:48,420
I wanna join.

484
00:29:48,460 --> 00:29:50,340
The choreography doesn't seem that hard.

485
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,430
Do me a favor, would you?

486
00:29:52,130 --> 00:29:53,460
Uh...

487
00:29:53,500 --> 00:29:54,940
Then who is going to hold the light?

488
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:57,190
But I do think

489
00:29:57,260 --> 00:29:58,390
it's a great idea.

490
00:29:58,620 --> 00:29:59,970
With the three of us,

491
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:01,600
it's going to be fun.

492
00:30:03,370 --> 00:30:04,370
Sure.

493
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:06,270
Let's give it a try, then.

494
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:08,180
Okay, everyone, let's dance.

495
00:30:08,250 --> 00:30:09,580
Music!

496
00:30:19,770 --> 00:30:21,860
Five, six, seven, eight...

497
00:30:30,120 --> 00:30:31,120
Meow...

498
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,900
Mm-hm...

499
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:36,290
A dog-sized cat.

500
00:31:06,970 --> 00:31:07,970
- Uh...
- I'm fine.

501
00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:09,800
It's hot here.

502
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,730
I think that's enough exercise for today.

503
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:14,130
Alright, everyone,
remember to come to Golden Peony Hotel.

504
00:31:14,230 --> 00:31:15,000
Bye-bye.

505
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,170
Ugh, the light!

506
00:31:16,770 --> 00:31:18,130
The livestream is over!

507
00:31:18,630 --> 00:31:19,660
You, too!

508
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:20,530
Turn off the light!

509
00:31:20,570 --> 00:31:22,220
Yes, I'll turn it off.

510
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,650
Let me go already!

511
00:31:26,140 --> 00:31:27,140
I thought you liked it.

512
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:29,880
You were lost in it.

513
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,400
Why are you here?

514
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:12,710
This is a staff-only zone.

515
00:32:14,930 --> 00:32:16,530
You're still into Fu, right?

516
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:20,480
What are you saying?

517
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:22,840
Let me rephrase.

518
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:24,870
What is Fu

519
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:26,880
to you?

520
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:30,040
Well...

521
00:32:30,700 --> 00:32:32,000
he's my friend's brother.

522
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:36,930
This BS again?

523
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,740
I see you're still as irritating as ever.

524
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:48,920
Don't ever let your guard down.

525
00:32:50,130 --> 00:32:51,690
He might still follow you around today,

526
00:32:53,170 --> 00:32:55,170
but it's not like
he would keep doing this forever.

527
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:58,700
Stop being so selfish.

528
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:22,140
Fu...

529
00:33:28,420 --> 00:33:29,960
Don't say those things to Moo.

530
00:33:31,280 --> 00:33:32,680
I'm the one pursuing him.

531
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:34,600
He didn't have anything to do with it.

532
00:33:40,020 --> 00:33:41,020
Fu,

533
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:44,000
so you chase after him

534
00:33:45,530 --> 00:33:47,730
even when he doesn't see your worth at all?

535
00:33:49,610 --> 00:33:50,610
And this

536
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:53,240
is not your concern at all, Kluayhom.

537
00:33:53,780 --> 00:33:54,780
It is.

538
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:57,290
Because I like you!

539
00:33:58,170 --> 00:33:59,410
I've liked you for a long time,

540
00:33:59,670 --> 00:34:00,800
ever since we were little!

541
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,200
And where did that get me?

542
00:34:04,630 --> 00:34:05,730
You only care for Moo.

543
00:34:05,950 --> 00:34:07,230
You only have your eyes for him.

544
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:15,900
Fu...

545
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:23,320
Be honest with me.

546
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:29,210
For once, can you give me a chance?

547
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:33,700
Please?

548
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,670
Just once?

549
00:34:41,810 --> 00:34:42,810
Then...

550
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:46,280
Would you come meet me at my room tonight?

551
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:06,360
Why did you invite me
out here for a drink?

552
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,160
Someone broke your heart, Fu?

553
00:35:09,870 --> 00:35:10,870
Not yet.

554
00:35:14,230 --> 00:35:15,460
But I don't know.

555
00:35:20,380 --> 00:35:21,480
Is it about Moo?

556
00:35:21,770 --> 00:35:22,770
Tai,

557
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,930
how am I not good enough?

558
00:35:27,890 --> 00:35:29,300
I'm hot

559
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:30,750
