584
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,150
Yeah!

585
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,240
Just like that.

586
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:37,960
You're just...

587
00:37:38,770 --> 00:37:40,210
