- What about everything until now?

639
00:40:50,970 --> 00:40:53,440
Have you been seeing me
at the same time as him?

640
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,270
I don't see what's wrong with it.

641
00:40:55,610 --> 00:40:58,310
