- Drink up, drink up, drink up!
- Bottoms up, bottoms up, bottoms up!

672
00:42:44,680 --> 00:42:46,970
Bottoms up, bottoms up, bottoms up!

673
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:52,960
Ooh, here he goes!

674
00:42:59,690 --> 00:43:02,660
This is a fucking blast, my peeps!

675
00:43:23,790 --> 00:43:27,410
This is a fucking blast, my peeps!!

676
