691
00:44:13,145 --> 00:44:15,850
Mm, I heard he's going to be on a travel show!

692
00:44:16,240 --> 00:44:18,060
- Ooh!
- Really?!

693
00:44:19,120 --> 00:44:20,670
- He's amazing!
- Of course!

694
