I'm not giving up that easily.

729
00:46:46,940 --> 00:46:49,116
(About you and them,
are you gonna move on or keep going?)

730
00:46:49,140 --> 00:46:52,020
(I'm gonna keep going, of course.
(I'm not giving up that easily. Go, go!)

